===Noun===

'''the [[stone|Stone]] [[age|Age]]'''
#A broad [[prehistoric]] period during which humans widely used [[stone]] for [[toolmaking]].
#(''figurative, informal'') Any extremely [[primitive]] or [[undeveloped]] [[era]].
#(''figurative'') The time a particular field was introduced and was in its earliest stages of development.

